Titolo: I Get This Call Every Day

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: I Get This Call Every Day is a point-and-click video game developed, programmed, and published by Toronto-based developer David S Gallant. It was released for Microsoft Windows and OS X on December 21, 2012. It focuses on a call received by an employee of a customer service call centre; the player must navigate through the call without irritating the caller or breaking confidentiality laws. Gallant was fired from his job at a call centre as a direct result of publishing the game.

Genere: Point-and-click 

Valutazione: N/A
